"2012-07-05","vote_average":6.587,"backdrop_path":"/61O5T8LT32NMRomUusjFmABMVIn.jpg","original_title":"연가시","original_language":"ko"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1996,"adult":false,"title":"Lara Croft: Tomb Raider - The Cradle of Life","video":false,"overview":"Off the coast of the volcanic island of Santorini, the intrepid archaeologist Lara Croft makes the unexpected discovery of a pulsating golden orb able to guide its holder to the mythical Pandora's Box. As the legendary artifact contains ancient mysteries of unfathomable power - said to contain one of the deadliest plagues on Earth, Lara is tasked by MI6 to make sure it doesn't fall into the wrong hands. With the aid of former Marine turned mercenary Terry Sheridan, she travels the world in pursuit of the precious item in a race against time; she must beat the unscrupulous Nobel Prize-winning scientist turned bioterrorist, Jonathan Reiss, to it.","genre_ids":[12,28,14],"popularity":3.0858,"vote_count":4439,"poster_path":"/ylIEGeAr2ygSClK4FDj9mi2Ah22.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-21","vote_average":5.76,"backdrop_path":"/lyCPWvJJSLgUo62USdnvqOVJfGi.jpg","original_title":"Lara Croft: Tomb Raider - The Cradle of Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":10544,"adult":false,"title":"Ned Kelly","video":false,"overview":"After getting threatened by Kelly's friends and family, Constable Fitzpatrick places the blame on Ned Kelly and exaggerates what happened. With the biggest ever award available, Kelly and his gang set into the wild, to remain hidden from everyone who seeks them. Even if it means having his family arrested, the members of the Kelly Gang stay hidden and plan a way to get their names cleared.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,36],"popularity":4.3257,"vote_count":382,"poster_path":"/xmGQsMbXKELzD4n78uMoCsgJPi4.jpg","release_date":"2003-03-22","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/s7InPuEqbxTjuLUpIZeBX3R9uEA.jpg","original_title":"Ned Kelly","original_language":"en"},{"id":10551,"adult":false,"title":"Family Business","video":false,"overview":"Jessie is an aging career criminal who has been in more jails, fights, schemes, and lineups than just about anyone else. His son Vito, while currently on the straight and narrow, has had a fairly shady past and is indeed no stranger to illegal activity. They both have great hope for Adam, Vito's son and Jessie's grandson, who is bright, good-looking, and without a criminal past.","genre_ids":[80,18,35],"popularity":0.8099,"vote_count":270,"poster_path":"/nALlbKdoKxlvwx9LDglOHZj0hs9.jpg","release_date":"1989-12-06","vote_average":5.672,"backdrop_path":"/xVTt5RHaTAuCStfAVrOCPMWA1ye.jpg","original_title":"Family Business","original_language":"en"},{"id":10423,"adult":false,"title":"Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story","video":false,"overview":"This film is a glimpse into the life, love and the unconquerable spirit of the legendary Bruce Lee. From a childhood of rigorous martial arts training, Lee realizes his dream of opening his own kung-fu school in America. Before long, he is discovered by a Hollywood producer and begins a meteoric rise to fame and an all too short reign as one the most charismatic action heroes in cinema history.","genre_ids":[18,36,28],"popularity":3.5954,"vote_count":783,"poster_path":"/lxhsdC8wuGgQf0gKCt8wyHHxGcQ.jpg","release_date":"1993-05-07","vote_average":6.897,"backdrop_path":"/1pOp56fSV4XySjaGrhb6NPD2n4r.jpg","original_title":"Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story","original_language":"en"},{"id":10589,"adult":false,"title":"After the Sunset","video":false,"overview":"An FBI agent is suspicious of two master thieves, quietly enjoying their retirement near what may - or may not - be the biggest score of their careers.","genre_ids":[28,35,80,18],"popularity":2.5572,"vote_count":838,"poster_path":"/1mo3OdxeR6pLgAVt4a3cyvUUQri.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-12","vote_average":6.158,"backdrop_path":"/4aPNUEIcXK7ISOV6qiQpTekGQez.jpg","original_title":"After the Sunset","original_language":"en"},{"id":10753,"adult":false,"title":"Police Story 